==Tailoring==
Poppy can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[Tailoring#Pants|Pleated Skirt]]. [[File:Pleated Skirt.png|36px]] It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as an orange dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Notes==
*Poppies have an equal chance of being one of three different colors. Poppies of different colors will occupy different slots in inventory or chests. Three colors &times; four [[Crops#Crop Quality|quality]] levels = 12 possible spaces used.
:[[File:PoppyColors.png]]

